text: Bogusław Owczarek (born 11 July 1965) is a Polish equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Piotrków County
